arte superior o inferior. Gana el jugador cuya carta tenga el mayor coste de maná convertido.)_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('139400','Wellgabber Apothecary','LRW','Creature — Merfolk Cleric','C','{4}{W}','5','2','3',NULL,'{1}{W}: Prevent all damage that would be dealt to target tapped Merfolk or Kithkin creature this turn.','#_"You''ve discovered that boggarts bite, I see. And will the militia be chasing this lot? . . . Ah, you''re staying in town to avoid Nath''s hunt. Wise. Now this poultice . . ."_#',NULL,'Brandon Dorman','47','2','£10/1/2007: The targeted creature must be tapped when the ability is activated and when it resolves. It doesn’t need to remain tapped in between.£10/1/2007: Once the ability has resolved, all damage that would be dealt to that creature for the rest of the turn will be prevented, regardless of whether it’s tapped or untapped at the time that damage would be dealt.','W',NULL,'0.04','0.16','0.94',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'W','闲语药剂师','閒語藥劑師','Apothicaire du puits cancanier','Geschwätziger Apotheker','Farmacista Ciarliero','大喋りの薬剤師','Boticário Tagarela de Poço','Аптекарь, Колодезный Сплетник','Boticario charlatán del pozo',NULL,'生物～人鱼／僧侣','生物～人魚／僧侶','Créature : ondin et clerc','Kreatur — Meervolk, Kleriker','Creatura — Chierico Tritone','クリーチャー ― マーフォーク・クレリック','Criatura — Tritão Clérigo','Существо — Мерфолк Священник','Criatura — Clérigo Tritón',NULL,'{1}{W}：于本回合中，防止将对目标已横置的人鱼或洁英生物造成的所有伤害。','{1}{W}：於本回合中，防止將對目標已橫置的人魚或潔英生物造成的所有傷害。','{1}{W} : Prévenez, ce tour-ci, toutes les blessures qui devraient être infligées à la créature Ondin ou Sangami engagée ciblée.','{1}{W}: Verhindere alle Schadenspunkte, die in diesem Zug einer getappten Meervolkkreatur oder Kithkinkreatur deiner Wahl zugefügt würden.','{1}{W}: Previeni tutto il danno che verrebbe inflitto a una creatura Tritone o Kithkin TAPpata bersaglio in questo turno.','{1}{W}：タップ状態の、マーフォーク・クリーチャー１体かキスキン・ク